<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٥)</span> بَابُ التَّوْحِيدِ وَفَضَائِلِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٣٠:</span> مَا مَعْنَى التَّوْحِيدِ؟ وَمَا أَقْسَامُهُ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">التَّوْحِيدُ هُوَ:</span> إِفْرَادُ اللهِ تَعَالَى بِمَا يَخْتَصُّ بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَأَقْسَامُهُ ثَلَاثَةٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - تَوْحِيدُ الرُّبُوبِيَّةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - تَوْحِيدُ الْأُلُوهِيَّةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣ - تَوْحِيدُ الْأَسْمَاءِ وَالصِّفَاتِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٣١:</span> مَا مَعْنَى تَوْحِيدِ الرُّبُوبِيَّةِ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">تَوْحِيدُ الرُّبُوبِيَّةِ هُوَ:</span> إِفْرَادُ اللهِ تَعَالَى بِأَفْعَالِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَقِيلَ:</span> هُوَ إِفْرَادُ اللهِ تَعَالَى بِالْخَلْقِ وَالْمُلْكِ وَالتَّدْبِيرِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>* * *<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>